Ruke gore!!

24
00:08:15,874 --> 00:08:16,890
-Na koljena !!
-Ne!!!

25
00:08:19,549 --> 00:08:20,565
Ne !!!

26
00:08:25,543 --> 00:08:28,120
Neki od nas su otišli.

27
